subject: Golf
lead_paragraph: Jesper Parnevik moved a step closer to his first PGA Tour victory in six and a half years, shooting a four-under-par 66 to take a three-stroke lead into the final round of the Texas Open in San Antonio. Parnevik had six birdies, with only two of the putts from more than 10 feet.
